TITLE: Chat Provider Setup (App) - TSX
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to use the Chat provider at the App level, wrapping your components and providing the Stream Chat client instance. The Chat provider is crucial for context sharing between Stream Chat components.
SOURCE: https://github.com/getstream/stream-chat-react-native/blob/develop/docusaurus/docs/reactnative/basics/hello_stream_chat.mdx#_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
import { StreamChat } from 'stream-chat';
import { Chat, OverlayProvider } from 'stream-chat-react-native';

const client = StreamChat.getInstance('api_key');

export const App = () => (
  <OverlayProvider>
    <Chat client={client}>{/** App components */}</Chat>
  </OverlayProvider>
);
```

