TITLE: Integrating Thread component in React Native
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to integrate the Thread component for threaded messages. It uses the onThreadSelect prop of MessageList to manage the selected thread. The thread state is maintained using useState and passed to the Channel component.
