TITLE: Initializing Stream Chat and Channel - React Native
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates the basic usage of the Channel component. It initializes a StreamChat client, creates and watches a channel, and renders the MessageList and MessageInput components within the Channel component. The channel state is managed using the useState hook.
SOURCE: https://github.com/getstream/stream-chat-react-native/blob/develop/docusaurus/reactnative_versioned_docs/version-3.x.x/core-components/channel.mdx#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: tsx
