TITLE: Register Device with Stream for Push Notifications
DESCRIPTION: Registers a device with Stream to receive push notifications by obtaining the Firebase device token and calling `client.addDevice`. This function also requests push notification permissions from the user. The `onTokenRefresh` listener ensures the device token is updated if it changes.
