TITLE: Wallpaper Overview Screen Implementation - TSX
DESCRIPTION: This snippet implements the WallpaperOverviewScreen, which allows the user to select a background image from a predefined list. It uses react-native-mmkv to store the selected image URI for the channel. It uses react-navigation to navigate back to the ChannelScreen after selection.  It depends on react-native-mmkv, react-navigation and react-native.
SOURCE: https://github.com/getstream/stream-chat-react-native/blob/develop/docusaurus/docs/reactnative/guides/custom-channel-background.mdx#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: tsx
